---
title: Golden Crumbed Salmon and Broccoli with buttered rice and lemony mayo
description: In this recipe, simple ingredients really shine. A lemony mayo works perfectly with the breaded salmon and roasted broccoli while butter adds new depth and dimension to the side of fluffy rice.
